The paper deals with the problem of expected cost analysis of probabilistic programs, which involves analyzing the resource usage of programs. This problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including programming languages (cs.PL), logic (cs.LO), data structures (cs.DS), cryptography (cs.CR), and control systems (cs.SY). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
